Muhammadu Buhari for a forensic audit of the Niger Delta Development Commission, NDDC, calling for the immediate inauguration of the new board of the commission to superintend over its activities for a holistic review and reforms. Continue reading APC Chairmen applauds Buhari’s directive on audit of NDDC at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard